精神文明追求，是一個致命的大錯。<br />\n<br />\n世界上無&quot;中國人民族&quot;<br />\n亦無&quot;中華民族&quot;<br />\n因為&quot;中華民族&quot;亦只係由56個不同種族組成政治名詞<br />\n只有漢族 (中原)  藏族 疆族 滿族<br />\n百越族(壯族) 朝鮮族 俄羅斯族等大大小小56個不同種族<br />\n更加無所謂&quot;中國人&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"反中国人 = 汉奸<br />\n<br />\n咁係乜嘢民族? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414863705f439fab470e7a874179b9e101e4a457","tid":1030384,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:20:39.000Z","msg":"咁記仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a496496c2bd1cdd8bbc99dce0b7c8f88f8e4b10","tid":1030384,"uid":37697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d5353a236793d7abf686ecb2816bf3f92e27136","tid":1030384,"uid":31637,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:15:38.000Z","msg":"送句野比香港美國民主黨及一眾左膠<br />\n魔鬼之路，可以由善意鋪成－《刑警》"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"陶傑講緊個d中國人就係你<br />\n<br />\n&quot;關懷社會貧窮階級的情懷和奉獻&quot; 就係你講既左膠"},{"pid":"6bde24691ca458aecb25297a9c59b8fd88027c7b","tid":1030384,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:24:34.000Z","msg":"呢條洋狗仲係度吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1cdaeae6151456874e9df891c4bc4b7760c0fe","tid":1030384,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T05:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a3ceddad4f88afcd8b2baf7e906d14e912275e","tid":1030384,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"真的講得幾清楚"},{"pid":"2114dfbd82ab0f046e986aab6ee80edcc171d461","tid":1030384,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:58:18.000Z","msg":"當年講東講西班主持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}